    "en": {
      "title": "Devdat's son killed his father and beat his mother",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mt. Police say that the father died and the mother was injured after being hit by a stick by the 47-year-old unmarried son.",
        "The person who has been murdered is Weligoda Noel De Silva, a 70-year-old father of two who resided in Galukissa Gallupara.",
        "Police say that the victim was paralyzed and lying on the bed and the suspect hit him on the head and he died on the bed.",
        "A police officer said that the investigation further revealed that the arrested suspect has been receiving treatment for a mental disorder for a long time."
      ],
